Detailed Description

cvmx_fpa_fpf8_size

FPA_FPF8_SIZE = FPA's Queue 8 Free Page FIFO Size

The number of page pointers that will be kept local to the FPA for this Queue. FPA Queues are assigned in order from Queue 0 to Queue 7, though only Queue 0 through Queue x can be used. The sum of the 9 (0-8) FPA_FPF::_SIZE registers must be limited to 2048.
